text:
Hello, Does anyone know why this appears in the URL of my website that is not hosted on HubSpot, and how to remove it? Thank you very much.
      /*?hsCtaTracking=271...*
Most likely you've clicked on a HubSpot CTA which lead you to this site. The `hsCtaTracking...`  is used for stats inside HS

Yes, but it is not a call to action. The link appears in the search results and when you click on it, it loads with the tracking code. Is it because I am redirecting an old HubSpot landing page to a new external landing page?
